# Session 007 – Relationship

## Goal

Define the Relationship concept.

---

## Decisions

A Relationship represents the connection between one person and one dog.

The relationship consists of:

- Trust
- Communication
- Play
- Everyday Life
- Cooperation
- Emotional Connection

Trust and Emotional Connection are separate concepts.

Every relationship has a unique superpower.

Relationships are never compared or ranked.

DailyPaws helps every relationship grow from its own strengths.

